description: Bollywood Zing is an authentic Indian mobile food truck! Our mission is to give our customers restaurant quality food without the high-end restaurant prices. We feature fresh food, cooked mild to medium spiced to cater to general public. If you like it little spicier we will be happy to ZING IT to satisfy your taste buds.Are you new to Indian food? Not sure if you will like it? Will it be too spicy? No problem! Just ask us for a small sample before you place your order! We want you to be happy with your order?  Have questions about what the dishes are made of? Just ask!To give you a variety, we will occasionally be changing up our menu. So find us and see what's new!A little touch of…spice in your life!
name: Bollywood Zing
